narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you consider yourself an actor, then you should be taking this class. If you have a desire to become a better actor, this is the class to take.
I would definitely recommend it! I imagine that the content of the course depends a lot on what your specific class wants to focus on, but I really enjoyed it and learned a lot!

Advanced Acting is great for anyone interested and with each teacher offers a very different and, I've found, incredibly rewarding viewpoint. I particularly encourage people to take this class with Professor Margolin if they get a chance.
TAKE IT!! It's a comprehensive acting class, one of the few practical courses offered and Deb is one of the professors at Yale that you cannot miss the opportunity to take a class with.
